OL,3,CMore people can now apply for social
OL,4,Chousing in Jersey
OL,6,FDeputy Mezec said: "Until now, younger
OL,7,Fpeople without children have had no
OL,8,Fchoice but to pay high rents in the
OL,9,Fprivate sector and potentially live in
OL,10,Frental stress because they were
OL,11,Fexcluded from accessing social
OL,12,Fhousing."
OL,14,FHe added that Andium Homes, Jersey's
OL,15,Fsocial housing provider, has made
OL,16,Fthese changes possible by delivering
OL,17,Fmore properties.
