OL,3,CMore people can now apply for social
OL,4,Chousing in Jersey
OL,6,FThe move follows changes made in
OL,7,FSeptember 2023, where age restrictions
OL,8,Fwere lowered from 40 to 35 for those
OL,9,Fwithout children.
OL,11,FAnnual income restrictions were also
OL,12,Fwidened for those needing two to four-
OL,13,Fbed properties from #61,956 per year
OL,14,Ffor a single person with one child up
OL,15,Fto #92,079 for joint applicants with
OL,16,Fthree children or more.
OL,18,FThe minimum age for people with
OL,19,Fchildren to access social housing
OL,20,Fcontinues to be 18 years old.
